title: Piriform.CCleaner.Professional.v5.05.5176.Multilingual.Incl.Keym
description:
CCleaner is the number-one tool for cleaning your Windows PC. It
protects your privacy online and makes your computer faster and more
secure. CCleaner is easy to use and a small, fast download and user
interface has the modern look.

CCleaner is a system optimization and privacy tool. Removes unused
files from your system - allowing Windows to run faster and freeing up
valuable hard disk space. It also cleans traces of your online
activities such as your Internet history.

CCleaner can run from a USB thumbdrive and be installed/run on a
computer without a complicated setup process.

It is possible to specify files, folders and registry keys to ignore
from the cleaning process.

But the best part is that it's fast (normally taking less than a second
to run) and contains NO Spyware or Adware!


iNSTALL/REGiSTER NOTES
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

Install the application and add the following line into your
C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc\hosts file:
127.0.0.1 license.piriform.com

Use keymaker to register the application. You might need to run it as
administrator
